# Local dev secrets for `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in.
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored; never commit real keys.

# Anthropic API key for the in-sandbox `claude` CLI. Injected into the sandbox
# env via the workspace `secrets` (never persisted to logs/snapshots).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional: an OAuth token instead of an API key (set one or the other).
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# Local dev needs NO host config. The container reaches the Worker's tool-bridge at
# `host.docker.internal:3001`, and preview URLs use a Cloudflare quick tunnel
# (`*.trycloudflare.com`) served from inside the sandbox — no tunnel setup, no
# custom domain, local or deployed. These vars are only OVERRIDES:
#
# PUBLIC_HOSTNAME  — pin the container→Worker bridge host (e.g. a stable named
#                    tunnel). Unset → host.docker.internal locally.
# PREVIEW_HOSTNAME — ONLY for the optional `exposePort`-fronted preview path (Worker
#                    serves the preview on a custom domain). Not needed for the
#                    default quick-tunnel previews. Requires a `*.<domain>` route.
# PUBLIC_HOSTNAME=your-host.example.com
# PREVIEW_HOSTNAME=preview.example.com
